            <h1 class="page-header">Lotus Tarot Privacy Policy</h1>
            <!-- <h4>
    We dislike unrequested marketing as much as you do!</h4>
<p>
    We promise never to share your email address, your name, your details or anything else you give us <em>with anyone at all!</em></p>
<p>
    You will only ever receive emails from us when you have asked for them, with the exception of administration emails from the webmaster that concern your particular Lotus Tarot account.</p>
